author: Graeme Campbell
title: Kate Moss Is the Latest Star to Flex in Louis Vuitton x Supreme
text:
Just a week after A$AP Rocky was captured flexin’ in some bold Supreme x Louis Vuitton pants, Kate Moss is the latest star to rep the upcoming collaboration.
Of course, us mere mortals won’t be able to get our hands on the garb until July at the earliest, but release dates don’t really apply when you’re one of the most famous models of all time and who goes by the nickname of “The Boss.” In an Instagram image posted by LV artistic director Kim Jones, Moss can be seen sporting a sure-to-be gold dust bogo with subtle LV monogram branding.
Kate the great #louisvuitton #supreme 6 years ❤( personal photo by me ) 
A post shared by mrkimjones (@mrkimjones) on Mar 1, 2017 at 12:28pm PST 

The image harks to the classic Supreme x Kate Moss T-shirt that was released back in 2012 which, since its release, has gone on to reach streetwear grail status. Moss isn’t the first celeb to rock the latest top; Travis Scott was also seen wearing it at the Paris Fashion Men’s Fashion Week release.
@louisvuitton ON GO 
A post shared by flame (@travisscott) on Jan 19, 2017 at 8:01am PST 

Moss might vibe the new partnership, but NYC skaters say they feel betrayed by Supreme.
